  "system": {
    "fuid": "marchosias",
    "summary": {
      "value": "The most courageous and loyal among fallen celestials."
    },
    "featureType": "projectfu.arcanum",
    "data": {
      "merge": "<h3>Glyphclaws</h3><p>You are immune to <strong>shaken</strong> and <strong>weak</strong>.</p><p>Once per turn during a conflict, you may perform the <strong>Skill</strong> action to deal an amount of <strong>physical</strong> damage equal to <strong>【10 + twice the number of Heroic Skills you have acquired】</strong> to each of up to two enemies you can see. If you do and at least one of those enemies loses Hit Points due to this damage, you gain <strong>1 Glyph Point</strong>.</p><p>When this Arcanum is dismissed, you lose all <strong>Glyph Points</strong>.</p><hr><p><strong>Enemies Suffer:</strong> @DMG[10+2*$mcc physical]{Physical Damage}<br><strong>You Gain:</strong> @PROGRESS[glyph-points update 1]{Gain 1 Glyph Point}</p>",
      "pulse": "",
      "dismiss": "<h3>Seal of Fire</h3><p>You deal 30 <strong>fire</strong> damage to one enemy you can see; this damage ignores Immunities and Resistances. If you lost <strong>3 or more Glyph Points</strong> by dismissing this Arcanum, choose one option for this effect:</p><ul><li><p>It deals 10 extra damage.</p></li><li><p>It deals damage to each of up to two enemies you can see (instead of only one enemy).</p></li></ul><hr><p><strong>Enemy Suffers:</strong> @DMG[&step(30,40,50) fire]{30 Fire} or @DMG[&step(40,50,60) fire]{40 Fire}<br><strong>You Lose:</strong> @PROGRESS[glyph-points reset]{Lose All Glyph Points}</p>",
      "domains": "fire, loyalty, vigor"
    },
    "source": "FUBC36"
  },
